summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5911 for the improvement of Cloverdale Street from Renton Avenue to Rainier Avenue; by installing fire hydrants, under Ordinance No. 78010, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
